{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require energy companies to maintain a supply of analogue meters",
        "additional_details": "We ask the government to ensure that energy companies maintain a supply of analogue meters, to meet the ongoing demand of those wishing to not have smart meters installed.\r\n\r\nPeople can refuse to have smart meters installed. Therefore we believe a level of production of analogue meters needs to be maintained so as to help avoid an eventual in effect 'mandation' of smart meters through obsolescence of alternatives.\r\n",
        "background": "Some people don't wish to have smart meters installed for several reasons including concerns they have about privacy and health. ",
